result.notes: Search for Annex 1 habitats in the Poole to Lyme Bay area. Survey run by Envision Mapping Ltd. on behalf of Natural England in 2007 as part of the selection process for a set of Special Areas of Conservation in the region. Data set is derived from drop down video surveys carried out by Envision Mapping Ltd in September 2007. Full report produced by Envision and their survey results were used by Royal Haskoning (2008) and Natural England (2009) to select draft SACs for the region.
